                        <interp inst="t18420103-name-477" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES COLLIER</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in College-hill—I took the prisoner—he had this bag in his hand, and dropped it in the middle of the road.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I heard a cry of "Stop thief." There were a good many persons running. The policeman took hold of my collar, and said I had stolen a carpet bag. I said I knew nothing about it.</p>
